EXTRACTED VALUE: The task of the psychotherapist is to use her social brain to connect with and modify the brains of her clients.
Can't wait for the next novel and pleased to learn the fourth one is coming along.
Anyway, I've gone from wanting the series to hurry up and get better to being disappointed there isn't much more to go. Great stuff!
Patch was a difficult character, full of secrets, mysterious, sexy and ultimately the saviour but no doubt also has his dark terrible secrets.
If you buy this graphic novel, buy the original version as the colouring was probably the best thing about it.
